          <input type="hidden" id="teamCategory" name="teamCategory" required>
          <div class="time-info">‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏°‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏ô‡∏≥ ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡πá‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ</div>
